membership:
ECTA together with other associations specialized in Intellectual Property (APRAM, BMM, CITMA, GRUR, MARQUES and UNION-IP) is participating in the European Sister Associations. &#xd;
&#xd;
The above mentioned associations meet once per year in order to discuss the latest developments in the field of Intellectual Property.

memberOrga:
Membership categories and further information regarding membership can be found at: http://www.ecta.org/association/membership&#xd;
&#xd;
ECTA Council Membership and Management Committee Members are from EU countries only.&#xd;
&#xd;
Our Committee members are primarily European with some exceptions.&#xd;
&#xd;
Ordinary membership is open to nationals of EU countries only but Associate membership is open to countries outside of the EU.
